I have been having troubles launching League through my normal network. After click on the shortcut, it displays the logo, sits there for about a minute then crashes with the error message &#039;unable to connect to the HTTP server. Make sure...&#039; 
I have checked all my setting (both computer and router), reset the router (both soft and hard resets), done a RADS repatch, run as admin, set DNS for google, flushed my DNS cache, reset winsock, and replaced the RADS_user_kernel.exe. Yet I hotspot from my phone it works perfectly. 
I had no troubles at nearly 3am this morning playing in ascension. My ISP is TPG.
